      "description": "Looking for your next rewarding weekend project? This vehicle is the perfect starting point for anyone who loves a full restoration! While it currently requires extensive mechanical and cosmetic attention to return to the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity to build a car exactly how you want it. It's an honest fixer-upper with plenty of potential for the right enthusiast!",
