    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small door dings consistent with regular use, while the interior remains comfortable and free of major tears or stains. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, with a responsive engine and a solid transmission that shifts as it should. It is a reliable choice for a daily driver or a weekend cruiser, offering a great balance of performance and value without needing any immediate major repairs.",
